00:59:23.120 --> 00:59:24.820
So your relationships will be better.

00:59:24.820 --> 00:59:27.220
Your mindset will be better, right?

00:59:27.220 --> 00:59:30.100
So there's—it's connected in so many ways, I think.

00:59:30.100 --> 00:59:39.140
